          <p>Employers pay a separate income-related ZVW contribution (inkomensafhankelijke bijdrage ZVW) calculated as a percentage of your gross salary. This is a wage cost for the employer and is not deducted from your take-home pay, so it does not appear in this calculator's results. The employee-side of Dutch healthcare is handled entirely outside of the Box 1 income tax system.</p>

